Servings: 4-6 <!--more-->

Prep Time: 20 minutes 

Cook Time: 20 minutes 

Cuisine: American 

By: [Tressa](https://www.jamilghar.com/about/)

{{< start_recipe >}}

### How to Make Persimmon Cardamom Cookie

#### Ingredients 

For the Cookie: 

* 3/4 cup Coconut Flour 
* 4 tbsp Almond Flour, blanched 
* 1/4 cup Flaxmeal 
* 1 tbsp Psyllium Husk Powder 
* 1/2 tsp Salt 
* 1 tbsp Cardamom, ground, divided 
* 1/8 tsp Nutmeg
* 1 tsp Cinnamon, ground 
* 1/8 tsp Baking Soda
* 3 Foya Persimmons, divided coarsley
* 1 lemon, juice and zest 
* 1/2 cup Almond Milk 
* 2 tsbp Butter, softened 
* 1 tbsp Coconut Oil, room temperature  
* 1/2 cup Swerve Brown Sugar 
* 1/2 tsp Maple Extract 
* 1 1/2 tsp Vanilla Extract 

For the Frosting: 

* 3 tbsp Ghee 
* 1 tbsp Monk Fruit, granulated 
* 1 tsp Maple Extract 
* 1/4 cup Heavy Cream 
* 1/8 tsp Cardamom, ground 


